==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Sea ginger
<hw>Sea" gin"ger</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A hydroid
coral of the genus <gen>Millepora</gen>, especially <spn>Millepora
alcicornis</spn>, of the <geog>West Indies</geog> and
<state>Florida</state>. So called because it stings the tongue like
ginger.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sea girdles</ent>⟦br⟧
